        <h3>Pet Sitting Services</h3>
        <p>
            When you must be away we provide your pets with the same excellent care, devotion and attention you give them on a regular basis, while expertly caring for your home and property. We provide frequent communication and updates so you can relax and enjoy your trip, knowing your pets’ needs are well-cared for.
        </p>

        <p>
            We offer Live-In Service and Overnights. We also offer 120 – 60 – 45 – 30 or 20 Minute Visits. These visits can be done in any combination; once, twice or three times per day.
        </p>
        <h3>All Pet Sitting Services Include:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Love, attention and play time
            </li>
            <li>
                Dog walks
            </li>
            <li>
                Providing fresh food and water
            </li>
            <li>
                Scooping litter boxes and cleaning surrounding area
            </li>
            <li>
                Tidying up pet’s habitat
            </li>
            <li>
                Administration of medications
            </li>
            <li>
                Newspapers, flyers, packages and mail collected and brought inside
            </li>
            <li>
                Water plants inside or outdoor
            </li>
            <li>
                Lights and blinds alternated
            </li>
            <li>
                Trash and recycle bins taken in/out
            </li>
            <li>
                Clean-up after pets on walk or in yard
            </li>
            <li>
                Basic Pool Maintenance (add water and chlorine tablets as needed)
            </li>
            <li>
                Check your home and yard after storms
            </li>
            <li>
                And more…
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>Of course every visit includes Belly-Rubs and Ear (or Rear) Scratches at no additional charge.</p>

        <h3>Overnight Services</h3>
        <p>
            Allows your pets to enjoy the comfort and security of their own home while you’re away. We can provide specialized attention to puppies, special needs and elderly dogs. We offer three levels of Overnight Service for your pets and home to meet different needs. We will arrive by 8pm and stay until 7am. We can also add a mid-day potty break or walk. If you desire we can also provide an Extended Overnight where we will arrive earlier in the evening, usually by 5pm and stay over until 7 am. The above list of services is included in our Overnight Service.
        </p>

        <h3>Live-In Services</h3>
        <p>
            Our most comprehensive and stress-free service for you and your pets. This service includes the above list plus full time care for your home and pets. We will stay in your home each day with two three-hour breaks which allow us to care for our own homes, families and pets. We do ask you to please schedule this service two or more weeks in advance if possible.
        </p>

        <h3>Daily Service</h3>
        <h4>Potty 'N Play Breaks</h4>
        <p>
            Our 20 minute Potty ‘N Play Break is a daily service designed for pets that need be taken outside on a regular schedule for fresh air, change of environment and to potty. We use lots of patience, encouragement and praise, with any extra time spent for exploration and play. This service is very beneficial for seniors, puppies and other pets that tend to “get into trouble” whether from loneliness or boredom, but giving them some playtime to look forward to while you are at work.
        </p>

        <h4>Dog Walking</h4>
        <p>
            Imagine never getting to leave your house day after day. Even if you have a yard, dogs need daily exercise for both mental and physical stimulation. Special attention is given to customize our service, in close coordination with you, to give your pets an enjoyable outing, especially during the hot summer months in our Arizona Desert. We take special care that each pet is exercised safely and appropriately for his or her breed, age and individual personality.
        </p>

        <h3> Other Services:</h3>
        <h4>Horses</h4>
        <p>Please call to see if our services are a match for your horses’ needs. Available horse care visits are 30-45-60-120 Minute visits. We can provide Live-In or Overnight services as well.</p>

        <h4> Pet Express Taxi</h4>
        <p>
            The Pet Express can transport your pet to just about any destination you may need. Our service includes picking up and delivering needed pet supplies, getting your pet to the airport, veterinarian or groomer safely and on-time for their appointment. We can accompany your pet throughout the visit if desired. We can also coordinate communication between you and your vet or groomer, as needed. We will then return your pet home and get him or her settled in to their normal environment with fresh food and water to await your arrival.
        </p>

